    Task --> TaskStatusModel : uses current status
    TaskStatusModel --> TaskWorkflowTransition : allows transitions
    Task --> TaskAssignment : assigns work
    Task --> TaskApplication : receives applications
    Task --> TaskVersion : snapshots

    Task --> TaskEntity : mapped to domain
    ITaskRepository <|.. TaskRepositoryImpl : implements
    TaskApplicationMapper ..> TaskEntity : maps responses

